thread.title_full: Brushy Mountain Bee Farm reviewed by JAMES DALPIAZ

author: JAMES DALPIAZ
title: JAMES DALPIAZ
text: I ordered bee supplies, bee clothes and supers from Brushy on many occasions. Their customer service team along with their shipping department are a 10. I will buy from Brushy from now on because they have the total package of price, quality and customer service.
